headline: Death Clock Launches "Life Lab": An AI Health Concierge Democratizing Private-Doctor Level Care for the Mass Market
summary: Death Clock, the world's #1 longevity app, today announced the launch of Life Lab, an advanced AI health concierge designed to shift healthcare from reactive treatment to proactive prevention.
